<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 11:17:15 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>民意调查显示，许多以色列人认为内塔尼亚胡因政治原因拖延人质交易</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-04/ty-article/.premium/plurality-of-israelis-think-netanyahu-stalling-on-hostage-deal-over-politics-poll-shows/0000018e-086a-d5ee-a78e-38ea87de0000</link><description>民意调查显示，73% 的世俗以色列犹太人支持目前正在讨论的释放人质和停火协议，而传统犹太人和极端正统犹太人的这一比例分别为 52% 和 24%</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 09:37:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-04/ty-article/.premium/plurality-of-israelis-think-netanyahu-stalling-on-hostage-deal-over-politics-poll-shows/0000018e-086a-d5ee-a78e-38ea87de0000</guid></item><item><title>朱迪亚沙漠发现稀有硬币，命名为巴尔·科赫巴领导人“牧师以利亚泽”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/archaeology/2024-03-04/ty-article/rare-coin-naming-bar-kochba-leader-eleazer-the-priest-found-in-judean-desert/0000018e-089e-d5ee-a78e-38de5ddd0000</link><description>这枚硬币上刻有公元 132 年的日期，并用古希伯来文字刻有牧师的名字。它似乎是从以色列死海的一个山洞里掉下来的，犹太叛乱分子一直躲在那里躲避罗马人——他们手中的标枪可能是偷来的</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 09:08:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/archaeology/2024-03-04/ty-article/rare-coin-naming-bar-kochba-leader-eleazer-the-priest-found-in-judean-desert/0000018e-089e-d5ee-a78e-38de5ddd0000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯狙击手使用公开出售给伊朗的美制瞄准镜</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-03-04/ty-article/.premium/hamas-snipers-using-u-s-made-sights-sold-openly-to-iran/0000018e-05e6-d3bd-afce-b5e7279a0000</link><description>从加沙缴获的狙击步枪上发现了一家在伊朗有官方经销商的美国公司生产的望远镜瞄准镜。该公司指控中国诈骗</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 08:13:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-03-04/ty-article/.premium/hamas-snipers-using-u-s-made-sights-sold-openly-to-iran/0000018e-05e6-d3bd-afce-b5e7279a0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军官员：如果不改变加沙的援助分配，杀戮场面将重演</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-04/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-officials-warn-without-method-of-aid-distribution-gaza-killings-will-repeat/0000018e-06fb-d5ee-a78e-36fb21dd0000</link><description>100 多名巴勒斯坦人在等待人道主义援助时被杀，以色列国防军官员敦促政府考虑在没有哈马斯参与的情况下分发援助物资的新方式，包括通过巴勒斯坦商人或海上</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 04:19:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-04/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-officials-warn-without-method-of-aid-distribution-gaza-killings-will-repeat/0000018e-06fb-d5ee-a78e-36fb21dd0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列将人道主义援助作为加沙的战略武器，但没有制定战略</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-04/ty-article/.premium/israel-is-using-humanitarian-aid-as-a-strategic-weapon-without-a-strategy/0000018e-068b-d3bd-afce-b7cb1a610000</link><description>援助不仅以卡车数量或分配的资金来衡量，还需要基于交战各方之间协议的受保护道路和安全区域。但这些协议并不是免费的</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 04:19:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-04/ty-article/.premium/israel-is-using-humanitarian-aid-as-a-strategic-weapon-without-a-strategy/0000018e-068b-d3bd-afce-b7cb1a610000</guid></item><item><title>救援部门称，黎巴嫩反坦克导弹造成 1 人死亡、9 人受伤</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-04/ty-article-live/israel-strikes-hezbollah-targets-in-lebanon-gantz-kicks-off-u-s-visit/0000018e-0776-d822-a9ce-7ff77a760000</link><description>以色列北部反坦克导弹造成 1 人死亡、9 人受伤 ■ 哈马斯高级官员：释放人质，下周末可能达成停火协议 ■ 部长本尼·甘茨在华盛顿与美国高级官员开始一轮会谈 ■哈马斯卫生部称加沙死亡人数上升至 30,534 人</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 04:14:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-04/ty-article-live/israel-strikes-hezbollah-targets-in-lebanon-gantz-kicks-off-u-s-visit/0000018e-0776-d822-a9ce-7ff77a760000</guid></item><item><title>副总统卡马拉·哈里斯对以色列自 10 月 7 日以来在加沙的行动提出美国最严厉的谴责</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-04/ty-article/.premium/vp-kamala-harris-offers-harshest-u-s-rebuke-of-israels-actions-in-gaza-since-october-7/0000018e-06a7-d5ee-a78e-36e7dbff0000</link><description>迄今为止，在以色列针对哈马斯的战争中，哈里斯一直被拜登政府视为“黑脸”，但她周日的言论是美国言论的转折点</description><pubDate>Sun, 03 Mar 2024 23:56:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-04/ty-article/.premium/vp-kamala-harris-offers-harshest-u-s-rebuke-of-israels-actions-in-gaza-since-october-7/0000018e-06a7-d5ee-a78e-36e7dbff0000</guid></item><item><title>不是意识形态，而是个人：甘茨的美国之行凸显了对内塔尼亚胡的完全不信任</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-03/ty-article/.premium/not-ideological-personal-gantzs-u-s-visit-underscores-utter-distrust-in-netanyahu/0000018e-0606-d5ee-a78e-36c6523b0000</link><description>当内塔尼亚胡得知甘茨成功抢了他的车后，总理有两个选择：第一个是向他表示祝贺，并向旅行者提供消息，以便转发给华盛顿和唐宁街 10 号。第二个是，嗯，发狂</description><pubDate>Sun, 03 Mar 2024 20:59:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-03/ty-article/.premium/not-ideological-personal-gantzs-u-s-visit-underscores-utter-distrust-in-netanyahu/0000018e-0606-d5ee-a78e-36c6523b0000</guid></item><item><title>经过10年的努力，加沙的一名巴勒斯坦妇女生下了双胞胎。以色列的袭击杀死了他们两人</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-03/ty-article/.premium/after-10-years-of-trying-a-woman-in-gaza-had-twins-an-israeli-strike-killed-them-both/0000018e-055c-d3bd-afce-b5dff6ca0000</link><description>据幸存者和当地卫生官员称，以色列的袭击袭击了加沙南部拉法的一处房屋，造成 13 名家庭成员死亡，另有 9 人在废墟下失踪</description><pubDate>Sun, 03 Mar 2024 19:52:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-03/ty-article/.premium/after-10-years-of-trying-a-woman-in-gaza-had-twins-an-israeli-strike-killed-them-both/0000018e-055c-d3bd-afce-b5dff6ca0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队命名在加沙地带南部战斗中丧生的预备役人员</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-03/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-names-reserves-soldier-killed-in-southern-gaza-strip-fighting/0000018e-0596-d5ee-a78e-35d678300000</link><description>中士。来自佩塔提克瓦的 33 岁丹尼斯·叶基莫夫 (Dennis Yekimov) 少校于周六在汗尤尼斯被杀。 “我再也见不到你了，只在照片里。”你是世界上最好的父亲，”他的小女儿哀悼道</description><pubDate>Sun, 03 Mar 2024 19:50:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-03/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-names-reserves-soldier-killed-in-southern-gaza-strip-fighting/0000018e-0596-d5ee-a78e-35d678300000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯拒绝透露人质姓名后，以色列抵制在开罗举行的加沙谈判</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-03/ty-article/.premium/israel-boycotts-gaza-talks-in-cairo-after-hamas-rejects-demand-to-name-hostages/0000018e-05ba-df38-a98f-7fbe56e60000</link><description>以色列安全内阁的消息人士批评内塔尼亚胡要求获得在与哈马斯达成协议时释放的活着人质的完整名单。一位人士表示，“这不需要成为推进谈判的障碍”</description><pubDate>Sun, 03 Mar 2024 19:49:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-03/ty-article/.premium/israel-boycotts-gaza-talks-in-cairo-after-hamas-rejects-demand-to-name-hostages/0000018e-05ba-df38-a98f-7fbe56e60000</guid></item><item><title>正确阅读民意调查：大多数美国人支持以色列而不是哈马斯</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-03-03/ty-article/.highlight/read-the-polls-properly-most-americans-back-israel-over-hamas/0000018e-0552-d5dd-abce-cf7ad9680000</link><description>如果以色列人没有在以色列的每个新闻周期中一次又一次地被告知，反以色列、支持哈马斯的情绪正在席卷美国，吓坏那里的犹太人和以色列人呢？</description><pubDate>Sun, 03 Mar 2024 19:12:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-03-03/ty-article/.highlight/read-the-polls-properly-most-americans-back-israel-over-hamas/0000018e-0552-d5dd-abce-cf7ad9680000</guid></item><item><title>2500万年前的一次突变如何让人类失去了尾巴</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/science/2024-03-03/ty-article/how-a-single-mutation-25-million-years-ago-cost-humans-our-tails/0000018e-04ec-d5dd-abce-cfee635e0000</link><description>一项新的研究探讨了人类尾巴缺失背后的神秘遗传机制，一些人认为这可能是类人猿两足行走的关键</description><pubDate>Sun, 03 Mar 2024 18:04:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/science/2024-03-03/ty-article/how-a-single-mutation-25-million-years-ago-cost-humans-our-tails/0000018e-04ec-d5dd-abce-cfee635e0000</guid></item><item><title>战争中的以色列：您需要了解的信息 – 第 149 天</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-03-03/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-what-you-need-to-know-day-149/0000018e-0558-d5dd-abce-cf7a9a0e0000</link><description>在卡塔尔称哈马斯未能发送待释放俘虏名单后，以色列坚持派代表团前往开罗 ■ 哈马斯消息人士称，协议可能“在几天内达成” ■ 以色列国防军：对超过 115 名等待援助的加沙人死亡的初步调查发现，以色列军队并未袭击他们 ■ 以色列国家粮食安全委员会主席因加沙“极度饥饿”而呼吁停火 ■ 战争已持续 149 天，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Sun, 03 Mar 2024 17:45:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-03-03/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-what-you-need-to-know-day-149/0000018e-0558-d5dd-abce-cf7a9a0e0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军方没有意识到加沙地带因饥饿而造成大规模死亡的风险</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-03-03/ty-article/.premium/the-israeli-military-doesnt-grasp-the-risk-of-mass-death-by-starvation-in-gaza/0000018e-041f-dc7c-a3cf-4cffa3aa0000</link><description>针对等待援助卡车的巴勒斯坦人的枪击事件反映出他们对局势严重性的无知。尽管以色列无视人道主义组织的警告，但世界正在倾听</description><pubDate>Sun, 03 Mar 2024 17:19:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-03-03/ty-article/.premium/the-israeli-military-doesnt-grasp-the-risk-of-mass-death-by-starvation-in-gaza/0000018e-041f-dc7c-a3cf-4cffa3aa0000</guid></item><item><title>本格维尔镇压巴勒斯坦标志，以色列警方逮捕挥舞巴勒斯坦国旗的足球迷</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-03/ty-article/.premium/police-arrest-soccer-fan-waving-palestinian-flag-amid-crackdown-on-palestinian-emblems/0000018e-04ff-d6be-afff-44ff85670000</link><description>尽管极右翼国家安全部长伊塔马尔·本·格维尔（Itamar Ben-Gvir）努力使之成为非法行为，但在以色列，挥舞巴勒斯坦国旗并不是非法行为。据警方称，这名 18 岁粉丝在被释放前受到“严厉审问”</description><pubDate>Sun, 03 Mar 2024 16:48:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-03/ty-article/.premium/police-arrest-soccer-fan-waving-palestinian-flag-amid-crackdown-on-palestinian-emblems/0000018e-04ff-d6be-afff-44ff85670000</guid></item><item><title>重新生活需要时间：以色列士兵在加沙预备役后适应生活</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-03/ty-article-magazine/.premium/it-takes-time-to-live-again-israeli-soldiers-adjusting-to-life-after-gaza-reserve-duty/0000018e-049b-d6be-afff-44db8f030000</link><description>10月份，超过30万以色列人被征召入伍，其中许多人在战争中度过了前所未有的长时间远离家人的时光。三名战斗预备役军人讲述回国时“从100到0”的挑战</description><pubDate>Sun, 03 Mar 2024 16:24:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-03/ty-article-magazine/.premium/it-takes-time-to-live-again-israeli-soldiers-adjusting-to-life-after-gaza-reserve-duty/0000018e-049b-d6be-afff-44db8f030000</guid></item><item><title>他们购买了以色列的梦想之家。现在它们一文不值</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-03/ty-article-magazine/.premium/they-bought-their-israeli-dream-homes-now-theyre-worth-nothing/0000018d-fad6-da4e-adbf-faff939e0000</link><description>10 月 7 日事件的以色列幸存者分散在全国各地，仍在为荒凉地区被毁的房屋支付抵押贷款。银行坚称价值下跌是暂时的</description><pubDate>Sun, 03 Mar 2024 15:09:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-03/ty-article-magazine/.premium/they-bought-their-israeli-dream-homes-now-theyre-worth-nothing/0000018d-fad6-da4e-adbf-faff939e0000</guid></item><item><title>“我的观点是贝都因人、巴勒斯坦人和山顶青年之间没有太大区别”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-03/ty-article-magazine/.premium/i-thought-there-isnt-much-difference-between-bedouin-palestinians-and-hilltop-youth/0000018d-982d-d92c-a9ed-fbfdfaaa0000</link><description>以色列摄影师安妮·西敏·希特里特 (Anne Simin Shitrit) 放弃了宗教信仰，与定居者一起生活。在她的新展览中，她以您从未见过的方式展示了西岸青年</description><pubDate>Sun, 03 Mar 2024 15:08:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-03/ty-article-magazine/.premium/i-thought-there-isnt-much-difference-between-bedouin-palestinians-and-hilltop-youth/0000018d-982d-d92c-a9ed-fbfdfaaa0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列最高粮食安全官员以加沙“极度”饥饿为由呼吁停火</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-03/ty-article/.premium/citing-extreme-hunger-in-gaza-israels-top-food-security-official-calls-for-cease-fire/0000018e-048b-d6be-afff-44cbd45e0000</link><description>上届政府任命的粮食安全负责人罗尼·斯特里尔教授警告说，以色列是国际协议的缔约国，这些协议要求以色列保护战区平民的生命并遵守“明确的游戏规则”</description><pubDate>Sun, 03 Mar 2024 14:54:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-03/ty-article/.premium/citing-extreme-hunger-in-gaza-israels-top-food-security-official-calls-for-cease-fire/0000018e-048b-d6be-afff-44cbd45e0000</guid></item></channel></rss>